      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LIGHTNING LILY (1) turned in a plain run last time when eighth at this track over 411m behind Little Girl Gone (24.59) in a Grade 5. Comes through a solid form race last start. Looks the one to beat on her best form. SPLIT MINDS (2) jumped from an awkward draw and ran well to finish in the placings, beaten 3 lengths (17.78) at Taree Super Track in Grade 5. Has failed to finish in the placings from three starts here. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Can measure up. ACES DOUGAL (4) is a solid beginner and with a good start can clear the draw. Latest effort finished 6th on June 15 over 300m at Q Straight behind Name Of Love beaten 4 lengths (17.14) in a Grade 6. Looks well placed here and among the chances. SWEET MARNI MOO (3) can measure up with the right run.",
